Job Seekers
1. Job Portal System
Users: Job Seekers & Employers

Employers can post jobs, search resumes.

Job Seekers can apply to jobs, upload resume.

Use permissions to separate views/actions for job seekers & employers.

Add email notifications for job application status.

Extra: Show jobs using API, maybe integrate LinkedIn Jobs API.


